headline: J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. Announces Participation in the 2025 Wells Fargo Industrials & Materials Conference
summary: LOWELL, Ark., June 05, 2025--J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. (NASDAQ: JBHT) Chief Operating Officer and President of Highway and Final Mile Services Nick Hobbs and Executive Vice President and President of Dedicated Contract Services Brad Hicks will address the 2025 Wells Fargo Industrials & Materials Conference in Chicago, IL at 2:15pm CDT on Tuesday, June 10, 2025.
